\f0\b\fs84 \cf0 Directions
\f1\b0\fs26 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\ql\qnatural

\fs64 \cf0 Combine the rum, lime juice and syrup. Fill a cocktail shaker halfway with ice and fill two-thirds full with the cocktail mixture. Shake for 30 seconds and pour into frosted martini glasses. Serve ice cold.\
\
Note: to make sugar syrup, combine 1 cup sugar and 1 cup water in a sauce pan and bring to a boil. Reduce the heat and simmer until all the sugar is dissolved. Chill.\
